{"id":147,"parent_id":141,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":147,"title":"1 Corinthians 6","subtitle":"","short_title":"1 Cor.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/6","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 6"],[".studySummary",["i","Church members should not fight one another in the courts—The unrighteous will not be saved—True Saints are the temple of the Holy Ghost."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/6.1","order":"03.09.006.17177"},["b","1"],"Dare any of you, having a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"matter"],"against another, go to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"law"],"before the unjust, and not before the saints?"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/6.2","order":"03.09.006.17178"},["b","2"],"Do ye not know that the saints shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"judge"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"world"],"? and if the world shall be judged by you, are ye unworthy to judge the smallest matters?"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/6.3","order":"03.09.006.17179"},["b","3"],"Know ye not that we shall judge angels? how much more things that pertain to this life?"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/6.4","order":"03.09.006.17180"},["b","4"],"If then ye have judgments of things pertaining to this life, set them to judge who are least esteemed in the church."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/6.5","order":"03.09.006.17181"},["b","5"],"I speak to your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"shame"],". Is it so, that there is not a wise man among you? no, not one that shall be able to judge between his brethren?"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/6.6","order":"03.09.006.17182"},["b","6"],"But brother goeth to law with brother, and that before the unbelievers."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/6.7","order":"03.09.006.17183"},["b","7"],"Now therefore there is utterly a fault among you, because ye go to law one with another. Why do ye not rather take",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"wrong"],"? why do ye not rather",["i",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"suffer"],"yourselves to"],"be",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"defrauded"],"?"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/6.8","order":"03.09.006.17184"},["b","8"],"Nay, ye do wrong, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"defraud"],", and that",["i","your"],"brethren."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/6.9","order":"03.09.006.17185"},["b","9"],"Know ye not that the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"unrighteous"],"shall not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"inherit"],"the kingdom of God? Be not deceived: neither",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"fornicators"],", nor idolaters, nor",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_9d"},"adulterers"],", nor",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_9e"},"effeminate"],", nor",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_9f"},"abusers"],"of themselves with mankind,"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/6.10","order":"03.09.006.17186"},["b","10"],"Nor",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"thieves"],", nor covetous, nor",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"drunkards"],", nor",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"revilers"],", nor",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_10d"},"extortioners"],", shall inherit the kingdom of God."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/6.11","order":"03.09.006.17187"},["b","11"],"And such were some of you: but ye are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"washed"],", but ye are",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"sanctified"],", but ye are justified in the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"name"],"of the Lord Jesus, and by the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_11d"},"Spirit"],"of our God."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/6.12","order":"03.09.006.17188"},["b","12"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"All"],"things are lawful unto me, but all things are not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"expedient"],": all things are lawful for me, but I will not be brought under the power of any."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/6.13","order":"03.09.006.17189"},["b","13"],"Meats for the belly, and the belly for meats: but God shall destroy both it and them. Now the body",["i","is"],"not for",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"fornication"],", but for the Lord; and the Lord for the body."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/6.14","order":"03.09.006.17190"},["b","14"],"And God hath both raised up the Lord, and will also",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"raise up"],"us by his own power."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/6.15","order":"03.09.006.17191"},["b","15"],"Know ye not that your bodies are the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"members"],"of Christ? shall I then take the members of Christ, and make",["i","them"],"the members of an harlot? God forbid."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/6.16","order":"03.09.006.17192"},["b","16"],"What? know ye not that he which is joined to an harlot is one body? for two, saith he, shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"one"],"flesh."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/6.17","order":"03.09.006.17193"},["b","17"],"But he that is joined unto the Lord is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"one"],"spirit."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/6.18","order":"03.09.006.17194"},["b","18"],"Flee fornication. Every sin that a man doeth is without the body; but he that committeth fornication sinneth against his own body."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/6.19","order":"03.09.006.17195"},["b","19"],"What? know ye not that your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"body"],"is the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"temple"],"of the Holy Ghost",["i","which is"],"in you, which ye have of God, and ye are not your",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_19c"},"own"],"?"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/6.20","order":"03.09.006.17196"},["b","20"],"For ye are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"bought"],"with a price: therefore glorify God in your body, and in your spirit, which are God’s."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/6.1a","order":"03.09.006.17197"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.16"},"Ex. 18:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/6.1b","order":"03.09.006.17199"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/18.17"},"Matt. 18:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/5.12"},"1 Cor. 5:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/64.12.9-12"},"D&C 64:12 (9–12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/6.2a","order":"03.09.006.17201"},["b","2a"],"See",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/7.1a"},["span.small","JST"],"Matt. 7:1–2 (Matt. 7:1 note",["i","a"],")"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/7.22"},"Dan. 7:22"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/20.4"},"Rev. 20:4"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/judgment-the-last"},"TG Judgment, the Last"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/6.2b","order":"03.09.006.17203"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/world"},"TG World"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/6.5a","order":"03.09.006.17205"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/shame"},"TG Shame"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/6.7a","order":"03.09.006.17207"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/retribution"},"TG Retribution"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/6.7b","order":"03.09.006.17209"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/forbear"},"TG Forbear"],"."],["div",{"id":"7c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/6.7c","order":"03.09.006.17211"},["b","7c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/6.29.29-30"},"Luke 6:29 (29–30)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/6.8a","order":"03.09.006.17213"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/fraud"},"TG Fraud"],";",["a.s